OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FChair for the Borders Rail Marion
OL,7,FShort says everyone was 'euphoric'
OL,8,Fabout its comeback.
OL,10,FShe said: "It was a very important
OL,11,Fday, it was transformational for the
OL,12,Fpeople in the Borders to now secure a
OL,13,Ftransport connection at least to
OL,14,FTweedbank. Everybody was euphoric."
OL,16,FThe 35-mile route between Edinburgh
OL,17,FWaverley and Tweedbank cost nearly
OL,18,F#300 million and has, in many ways,
OL,19,Freshaped the region.
