OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FFor many, the new chapter brought new
OL,7,Fbusiness and opportunities. In Stow,
OL,8,FWedale Books owner Gordon Stewart says
OL,9,Fthe railway was central to his
OL,10,Fdecision to open a bookshop two years
OL,11,Fago.
OL,13,FHe said: "Having the railway for the
OL,14,Fbookshop was absolutely key. I think
OL,15,Fwe're the only independent bookshop
OL,16,Fthat you can reach directly by rail in
OL,17,Fthe Borders.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
