OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"We've got a series of events and
OL,7,Factivities, and all these are attended
OL,8,Fby people who come to us by rail, so
OL,9,Ffrom Newtongrange, from Gorebridge,
OL,10,Ffrom Galashiels, Tweedbank, as well as
OL,11,Fothers from further across the
OL,12,FBorders... the railway plays a huge
OL,13,Fpart in what we do."
OL,15,FThis village was not included in the
OL,16,Frailway's initial route; campaigners
OL,17,Ffought hard to put their home on the
OL,18,Frailway map.
