OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FSteven Herd moved to the village
OL,7,Fbecause the station enabled him to
OL,8,Fcommute to Edinburgh for work, while
OL,9,Fenjoying the rural landscape.
OL,11,FHe said: "We moved to Stow just over
OL,12,Fsix years ago, my wife and I had a
OL,13,Fyoung family, and we were living in
OL,14,FLeith in a flat.
OL,16,F"We decided to move down here because
OL,17,Fwe wanted to buy our own place to be
OL,18,Fable to afford to do that, and just to
OL,19,Fhave a better life for our young
OL,20,Ffamily at that time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
