OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"It was a massive factor to have the
OL,7,Fline in our move to Stow. For us,
OL,8,Fwe've both got careers in Edinburgh,
OL,9,Fwe've had them since we lived in
OL,10,FLeith, and we wanted to maintain
OL,11,Fthose, so being able to commute in and
OL,12,Fout in under 50 minutes was really
OL,13,Fimportant to us, so having that on
OL,14,Fyour doorstep was a huge factor for
OL,15,Fus."
OL,17,FThirteen million passengers have used
OL,18,Fthe Borders Railway since it opened a
OL,19,Fdecade ago.
