OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FIn Galashiels, the main transport
OL,7,Finterchange is home to one of the
OL,8,FBorders' main estate agents.
OL,10,FRoss Kilshaw, from Cullen Kilshaw
OL,11,FSolicitors and Estate Agents in
OL,12,FGalashiels, says the railway is
OL,13,Fundoubtedly a selling point for those
OL,14,Fseeking to buy property in the area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
