OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FHe added: "In the last ten years,
OL,7,Fsince the rail link came to the
OL,8,FBorders, property values have gone up
OL,9,Fsomething like 26% although actually,
OL,10,Fwhen you drill down into that, almost
OL,11,Fall of that gain has come since COVID,
OL,12,Fand so it looks like values were
OL,13,Fpretty flat from 2015 to 2019.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
