OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1757424805
OL,3,CA royal reopening of the railway line
OL,4,Cin the Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"But since COVID and post-pandemic,
OL,7,Fwith people relocating out to the
OL,8,Fcountry looking for green spaces and
OL,9,Fmaybe better lifestyles, we've seen
OL,10,Falmost all of that growth across all
OL,11,Fof the Borders, so we can't peel out
OL,12,Fhow much of that is towns linked to
OL,13,Fthe rail links.
OL,15,F"But I can only imagine that's been
OL,16,Fvery attractive to people who have
OL,17,Fbeen moving out of the city."
